      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MY BROTHERS ANGEL (2) proved too strong last start and scored by 4.5 lengths over 1408m at this track (Dirt). Has started two times at this course and distance and is yet to miss the placings. Should be poised just off the lead. Leading contender. MUSICAL STANDARD (1) ran below expectations when fresh from a spell at this track (Dirt) over 1308m last time, finishing fifth and beaten 21 lengths. Nicely placed to bounce back. FIBER PROOF (6) was out of the money two runs back then again missed the frame last start over 1408m at this track, beaten 7 lengths into fourth. Best figures measure up nicely. Sure to run well. LEGENDARY SKY (5) got off the mark over 1308m at this track (Dirt) last start, scoring by 0.8 lengths. Is lightly raced and has plenty of scope for improvement. Moises Santaella was in the saddle on that occasion and retains the ride. Harder task ahead this time but can measure up.",
